<paragraph id="D10D36F9990C2B3DBF23FE72FB32FC10" blockId="11.[826,1429,311,1433]" pageId="11" pageNumber="403">
Morphology — Male: Integument papillate (
<figureCitation id="49892A7C990C2B3DB926FE72FC5BFE57" captionStart="FIGURE" captionStartId="13.[159,171,1848,1867]" captionTargetBox="[243,1343,349,1816]" captionTargetId="figure-6@13.[242,1346,346,1816]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURE 7: Hygrobates (Hygrobates) henni Wiles, 2004, male, Kauangxi Waterfall, Laos: A – idiosoma, ventral view; B – details of dorsal integument; C – I-L-5 and -6; D – chelicera; E-F – palp. Scale bars – 100 µm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5395998" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5395998/files/figure.png" pageId="11" pageNumber="403">Figure 7B</figureCitation>
). Posteromedial margin of Cx-I broadly rounded. Cx-IV with a distinct nose-like protruding medial margin. Genital plate anterior margin with a small knob-shaped medial projection projecting in a deep indentation, posterior margin deeply indented with a small protrusion in the centre of indentation; acetabula in a triangular arrangement, Ac-2 and Ac- 3 on the same level (
<figureCitation id="49892A7C990C2B3DB868FD5BFB6DFD22" box="[1067,1188,677,701]" captionStart="FIGURE" captionStartId="13.[159,171,1848,1867]" captionTargetBox="[243,1343,349,1816]" captionTargetId="figure-6@13.[242,1346,346,1816]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURE 7: Hygrobates (Hygrobates) henni Wiles, 2004, male, Kauangxi Waterfall, Laos: A – idiosoma, ventral view; B – details of dorsal integument; C – I-L-5 and -6; D – chelicera; E-F – palp. Scale bars – 100 µm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5395998" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5395998/files/figure.png" pageId="11" pageNumber="403">Figure 7A</figureCitation>
). P-2 ventral margin proximally almost straight, distoventrally protruding in a long and slender projection, apically covered by a few small denticles; P-3 distally with 7- 8 larger denticles covering more than half of ventral margin (
<figureCitation id="49892A7C990C2B3DBF89FCAAFBFFFCF3" box="[970,1078,852,876]" captionStart="FIGURE" captionStartId="13.[159,171,1848,1867]" captionTargetBox="[243,1343,349,1816]" captionTargetId="figure-6@13.[242,1346,346,1816]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURE 7: Hygrobates (Hygrobates) henni Wiles, 2004, male, Kauangxi Waterfall, Laos: A – idiosoma, ventral view; B – details of dorsal integument; C – I-L-5 and -6; D – chelicera; E-F – palp. Scale bars – 100 µm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5395998" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5395998/files/figure.png" pageId="11" pageNumber="403">Figures 7</figureCitation>
E-F); P-4 slender, ventral setae close to each other (separation 22 µm).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D10D36F9990C2B3DBF23FC54FA9CFB45" blockId="11.[826,1429,311,1433]" pageId="11" pageNumber="403">
Measurements — Idiosoma L/W 713/637; coxal field L/W 331/522, Cx-III W 406; genital plate L/W 166/213, ratio 0.78; ejaculatory complex L 132. Palp: total L 378, dL/H, dL/H ratio: P-1, 30/36, 0.83; P- 2, 97/65, 1.5; P-3, 77/57, 1.35; P-4, 126/31, 4.1; P- 5, 48/16, 2.9; L ratio P-2/P-4, 0.77; chelicera total L 254, claw L 90, basal segment L 170, L basal segment/claw ratio 1.9. Legs: dL of I-L-5-6 (
<figureCitation id="49892A7C990C2B3DB951FB61FA40FB28" box="[1298,1417,1183,1207]" captionStart="FIGURE" captionStartId="13.[159,171,1848,1867]" captionTargetBox="[243,1343,349,1816]" captionTargetId="figure-6@13.[242,1346,346,1816]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURE 7: Hygrobates (Hygrobates) henni Wiles, 2004, male, Kauangxi Waterfall, Laos: A – idiosoma, ventral view; B – details of dorsal integument; C – I-L-5 and -6; D – chelicera; E-F – palp. Scale bars – 100 µm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5395998" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5395998/files/figure.png" pageId="11" pageNumber="403">Figure 7C</figureCitation>
): 135, 130; dL of IV-L: 113, 94, 131, 194, 213, 163.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D10D36F9990C2B3DBF23FB0BFCBFFA06" blockId="11.[826,1429,311,1433]" pageId="11" pageNumber="403">
Remarks — The single male from Kauangxi Waterfall matches the general morphology of 
<taxonomicName id="16B24D7A990C2B3DB904FAE7FB8CFACC" authority="Wiles, 2004" authorityName="Wiles" authorityYear="2004" class="Arachnida" family="Hygrobatidae" genus="Hygrobates" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="11" pageNumber="403" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="henni">
<emphasis id="E3C6EAEB990C2B3DB904FAE7FC7CFACC" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="403">Hygrobates henni</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="B5234B08990C2B3DBFFEFAC5FB8CFACC" author="Wiles P. R." box="[957,1093,1339,1363]" pageId="11" pageNumber="403" pagination="2153 - 2165" refId="ref17064" refString="Wiles P. R. 2004 - Water mites (Acari: Hydrachnidia) from South-East Asia, Thailand and Sulawesi Tenggara (Indonesia): descriptions of new species and new records - J. Nat. Hist., 38: 2153 - 2165." type="journal article" year="2004">Wiles, 2004</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. This species was described by 
<bibRefCitation id="B5234B08990C2B3DBF21FAA0FC3DFAE9" author="Wiles P. R." box="[866,1012,1374,1398]" pageId="11" pageNumber="403" pagination="2153 - 2165" refId="ref17064" refString="Wiles P. R. 2004 - Water mites (Acari: Hydrachnidia) from South-East Asia, Thailand and Sulawesi Tenggara (Indonesia): descriptions of new species and new records - J. Nat. Hist., 38: 2153 - 2165." type="journal article" year="2004">Wiles (2004)</bibRefCitation>
from Mai Yim waterfalls in 
<collectingCountry id="A9A57669990C2B3DB914FAA0FCBBFA06" name="Thailand" pageId="11" pageNumber="403">Thailand</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D10D36F9990C2B3DBF23FA4AFCB1F98E" blockId="11.[826,1429,1460,1553]" pageId="11" pageNumber="403">
Distribution — Previously known only from 
<collectingCountry id="A9A57669990C2B3DBF79FA29FC6FFA70" box="[826,934,1495,1519]" name="Thailand" pageId="11" pageNumber="403">Thailand</collectingCountry>
, and here reported for the first time for 
<collectingCountry id="A9A57669990C2B3DBF79FA04FCBDF98E" box="[826,884,1530,1553]" name="Laos" pageId="11" pageNumber="403">Laos</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
